thread.title: A New Jersey Development Offers Sweeping Views of Manhattan—and More for a Buyer’s Money

author: Josh Barbanel
title: A New Jersey Development Offers Sweeping Views of Manhattan—and More for a Buyer’s Money
text:
What is a Manhattan view worth?
One developer in West New York, N.J., is hoping a new penthouse apartment with a dead-on vista of Midtown from the shore of the Hudson River can command $8 million.
